OL,6,FFood sales were up 2.9% year on year
OL,7,Fover the three months to August,
OL,8,Fagainst growth of 8.2% for the same
OL,9,Fperiod last year, and below the 12-
OL,10,Fmonth average growth of 5%.
OL,12,FNon-food sales were down 1.7% year on
OL,13,Fyear over the quarter against a
OL,14,Fdecline of 0.2% last year.
OL,16,FIn-store non-food sales were down 2.8%
OL,17,Fover the quarter on last year against
OL,18,Fgrowth of 1.3% last August.
