OL,4,Cretail sales rise by 1% on last August
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Sales growth picked up in
OL,8,FAugust, particularly for food as
OL,9,Fpeople came together to host barbecue
OL,10,Fand picnic gatherings for family and
OL,11,Ffriends, and for summer clothing,
OL,12,Fhealth and beauty products as people
OL,13,Fprepared for trips away and summer
OL,14,Fsocial events.
