OL,3,CFragile consumer confidence sees
OL,4,Cretail sales rise by 1% on last August
OL,6,F"While computing did well as
OL,7,Funiversity students made the most of
OL,8,Fsummer discounting and readied
OL,9,Fthemselves for the new academic year,
OL,10,Fother back-to-school related sales
OL,11,Fwere weaker than normal as some
OL,12,Ffamilies opted for second-hand
OL,13,Fpurchases.
OL,15,F"Following a difficult summer for much
OL,16,Fof retail, and the possible weakening
OL,17,Fof consumer spending as energy bills
OL,18,Frise come October, many will be
OL,19,Fwaiting for the Chancellor's Autumn
OL,20,FBudget before finalising their
OL,21,Finvestment strategies."
