OL,3,CFragile consumer confidence sees
OL,4,Cretail sales rise by 1% on last August
OL,6,FLinda Ellett, UK head of consumer
OL,7,Fretail and leisure at KPMG, said:
OL,8,F"Despite summer finally making an
OL,9,Fappearance, and a slight uptick in
OL,10,Fconsumer confidence, shoppers did not
OL,11,Fcatch up their spending during August,
OL,12,Fwith total sales growth of only 1%
OL,13,Freflecting the challenging retail
OL,14,Fenvironment that is likely to dominate
OL,15,Ffor the rest of this year.
