OL,3,CFragile consumer confidence sees
OL,4,Cretail sales rise by 1% on last August
OL,6,F"Consumer sentiment is gradually
OL,7,Fstarting to improve, but there still
OL,8,Fremains some nervousness around
OL,9,Fpotential tax rises and the cost of
OL,10,Fputting the heating back on when the
OL,11,Fcooler weather arrives.
OL,13,F"The fragile nature of consumer
OL,14,Fconfidence means shoppers will
OL,15,Fcontinue to be driven by price and
OL,16,Fvalue, moving from brand to brand to
OL,17,Ffind the best price benefit and we are
OL,18,Flikely to see retailers using
OL,19,Fpromotional activity to seek to win at
OL,20,Fthis."
